-- Convoy Cleanup: Archive completed convoys and notify overseer.
-- Dog receives convoy ID via hook, generates summary, archives, notifies Mayor.

## convoy-cleanup {
  input param.convoy : str required

  squash>
    trigger: on_complete
    template: work
    include_metrics: true

  # load-convoy : script
    @retry(max: 2)
    user>
      Load convoy and verify it is complete (all tracked issues closed).
    ```bash
    gt hook
    bd show {{param.convoy}} --json
    BLOCKED=$(bd blocked {{param.convoy}} --json 2>/dev/null || echo "[]")
    echo "$BLOCKED" | jq 'if length == 0 then "VERIFIED" else "NOT_READY" end'
    ```
  #/

  # generate-summary : llm
    - load-convoy
    @retry(max: 2)
    system>
      You summarize completed convoy work for overseer reporting.
    context>
      Convoy details: {{load-convoy}}
    user>
      Generate a concise convoy summary including:
      - Duration (start to finish)
      - Issues by type (task, bug, feature)
      - Contributors (unique assignees)
      - Key outcomes
    format> json
      { "duration": str, "issue_count": number,
        "contributors": [str], "summary_md": str }
  #/

  # archive-convoy : script
    - generate-summary
    user>
      Close the convoy bead and sync.
    ```bash
    bd close {{param.convoy}} --reason="Convoy complete"
    bd sync
    bd show {{param.convoy}} --json | jq '.status'
    ```
  #/

  # notify-overseer : script
    - archive-convoy
    - generate-summary
    user>
      Send completion mail to Mayor and verify activity feed.
    ```bash
    gt mail send mayor/ \
      -s "Convoy complete: {{param.convoy}}" \
      -m "Convoy {{param.convoy}} archived.

{{generate-summary}}"

    gt feed --since 5m
    ```
  #/

  # return-to-kennel : script
    - notify-overseer
    user>
      Signal DOG_DONE to Deacon.
    ```bash
    gt mail send deacon/ -s "DOG_DONE $(hostname)" -m "Task: convoy-cleanup
Convoy: {{param.convoy}}
Status: COMPLETE
Ready for next assignment."
    ```
  #/

  load-convoy -> generate-summary -> archive-convoy -> notify-overseer
  notify-overseer -> return-to-kennel
##/
